description:
Luffy`s daring assault on the venomous warden of Impel Down leaves him struggling to stand up, but despite the lethal poison breaking down his body, the rubber-man kicks his rescue mission into second gear!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Le combat s`achève. Luffy lance une dernière attaque au péril de sa vie !
Shiyuu Kessu! Sutemi no Luffy Saigo no Ichigeki
The Showdown Has Come! Luffy`s Desperate Last Attack!
آن أوان النّزال! هجوم لوفي الأخير اليائس!
雌雄決す! 捨て身のルフィ最後の一撃
